{"tid":1823607,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰「鼓勵」放無薪假     稱讓員工發展公餘興趣","createTime":"2020-01-14T00:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T17:05:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75c5d0c45fcf81cdbac0c11f6f5933f6e074d4c0","tid":1823607,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T00:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eNZo2kq29kLv4lfyw9TNdw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-01/1643b270-35cb-11ea-bff5-aee8f1a67048\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FeNZo2kq29kLv4lfyw9TNdw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-01%2F1643b270-35cb-11ea-bff5-aee8f1a67048&h=934a0044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰稱沒有要求員工強制性放取無薪假。<br />\n<br />\n訪港旅客大減，相關行業的生意大受影響。因管理不善而從全球最佳航空公司排名跌出三甲的國泰航空亦要控制成本，去年已宣布削減部分航班，今年有傳考慮計劃鼓勵員工放無薪假，假期甚至可長達一個月。國泰回覆東網查詢稱，並沒有要求任何國泰及國泰港龍航空員工強制性放取無薪假。<br />\n<br />\n國泰稱，國泰及國泰港龍航空有為機組人員提供純自願性質、平衡工作及生活的「靈活執勤安排」。機組人員可申請此執勤安排，發展公餘的其他興趣，同時保持均衡的生活方式。<br />\n<br />\n至於被問及會否裁員，過去半年縮減航班及削減人手的數目，國泰則未有回應。"},{"pid":"bf2e00e3756e5f53036e7d05c806ca49eb92f419","tid":1823607,"uid":159876,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T00:22:02.000Z","msg":"咁又公道d 講句，人地公司無強迫就No say 既。平時好景個陣，放無薪假你估咁易嫁咩，而家咪當共渡時艱囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ec22e3339fca152a662fa49c6ec3b6299b1748","tid":1823607,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T00:22:05.000Z","msg":"等執笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同tvb一樣"},{"pid":"ae7fa730ee49878caf35c69980b085f80ba66381","tid":1823607,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf2e00e3756e5f53036e7d05c806ca49eb92f419","tid":1823607,"uid":159876,"like":1,"disli